Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要念  不許念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不對勁啊
